# Scary Esports

**Free Fire tournaments & paid scrims platform with leaderboard, OTP login, referral & Razorpay payments**

---

## 🔥 Features

- Player & Admin roles
- Tournament creation & management (admin only)
- Leaderboards with points for kills & booyahs
- Paid scrims using Razorpay
- Email OTP login
- Referral system & user balance
- Responsive frontend (React)
- Backend API (Node.js + Express)
- MongoDB database (Atlas or local)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, React Router, Axios
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express, JWT Authentication
- **Database:** MongoDB (Atlas or local)
- **Payments:** Razorpay integration
- **Email OTP:** Nodemailer

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+
- MongoDB running locally or Atlas cluster
- Razorpay account for test/live payments
- Gmail account (or SMTP) for OTP emails

---

### Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# edit .env with your keys and secrets
npm install
npm run dev
